00:02:36.092 --> 00:02:37.546
I ain't gonna lie to you.

00:02:38.850 --> 00:02:41.963
EA: Estimates of how many innocent
people are locked up

00:02:41.987 --> 00:02:44.677
range between one and four percent,

00:02:44.701 --> 00:02:46.707
which maybe doesn't sound like a lot,

00:02:46.731 --> 00:02:50.916
except that it amounts
to around 87,000 people:

00:02:50.940 --> 00:02:54.314
mothers, fathers, sons locked up,

00:02:54.338 --> 00:02:55.687
often for decades,

00:02:55.711 --> 00:02:57.917
for crimes they did not commit.

00:02:57.941 --> 00:03:01.013
